==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Antiqueness
<hw>An*tique"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being antique;
an appearance of ancient origin and workmanship.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>We may discover something venerable in the <qex>antiqueness</qex>
of the work.</q> <rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Antiquist</ent>⟦br⟧
